1.6
log
@Add SGMII support and PHY addresses for 8-port EdgeRouters. This makes
plain RJ45 ports eth[4-7] usable.

ok dlg@@, tested by martijn@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: cn30xxgmxvar.h,v 1.5 2015/09/14 11:18:49 stsp Exp $	*/

